y-center pointer-events-none"><div class="flex w-full h-12 items-center justify-center pointer-events-none"><div class="ml-0.5 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg h-8 pl-2 pr-2.5 text-center font-small sm:font-base text-text-500 select-none transition-opacity duration-150 pointer-events-auto bg-bg-300">Free plan<div class="size-[3px] bg-text-500/30 rounded-full mt-0.5"></div><span><a href="https://claude.ai/upgrade" class="inline underline underline-offset-[3px] [&amp;:not(:is(:hover,:focus))]:decoration-[color-mix(in_srgb,currentColor,transparent_60%)] cursor-pointer">Upgrade</a></span><button type="button" aria-label="Dismiss upgrade banner" class="ml-1 -mr-1 flex size-5 items-center justify-center rounded-[4px] hover:bg-bg-400 transition-colors"><div style="width: 14px; height: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.147 4.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .707.707L10.707 10l5.147 5.147a.5.5 0 0 1-.63.771l-.078-.064L10 10.707l-5.146 5.147a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.707L9.293 10 4.146 4.853a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.707L10 9.293z"></path></svg></div></button></div></div></div></div></header><div class="overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden [scrollbar-gutter:stable] pt-6 flex-1 print:!overflow-visible print:!h-auto" data-autoscroll-container="true" style="overflow-anchor: none;"><div class="relative w-full min-h-full flex flex-col"><div class="mx-auto flex w-full flex-1 flex-col max-w-3xl md:px-2"><div role="status" class="sr-only">Claude finished the response</div><div class="flex-1 flex flex-col px-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full pt-1"><div role="feed" aria-label="Chat messages" aria-describedby="_r_3v_" aria-busy="false" data-find-provider-scope="" style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><p id="_r_3v_" class="sr-only select-none">Use the up and down arrow keys to move between messages.</p><div data-sizer-excess="0" style="height: 10224px; width: 100%; position: relative;"><button type="button" class="sr-only select-none" tabindex="-1">Load earlier messages</button><div data-index="21" style="position: absolute; top: 6398px; left: 0px; width: 100%;"><div role="article" tabindex="0" aria-setsize="32" aria-posinset="22" aria-label="Message 22 of 32"><div data-test-render-count="1"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-[var(--msg-assistant-pb,0.75rem)]" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><h2 data-find-omitted="" class="sr-only select-none">Claude responded: Since you work solo, this set of questions is really aimed at a team/organization context — Enterprise Search is built around colleagues, shared docs, and org-…</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Since you work solo, this set of questions is really aimed at a team/organization context — Enterprise Search is built around colleagues, shared docs, and org-wide communications, none of which apply to your workflow right now. Here's how I'd honestly answer them for your situation:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>What questions do you frequently ask colleagues that could be answered by searching your organization's documents and communications?</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Not applicable — you don't have colleagues or shared org documents in this workflow. Your process is self-contained: ideas come from live brainstorming, feedback comes from Claude, and outputs land in your own notes app.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Are there onboarding or training scenarios where Enterprise Search could help new team members get up to speed faster?</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Not applicable currently, since there's no team to onboard. If that changes later — say you bring on a collaborator or start a team version of this idea-narrowing process — Enterprise Search would become relevant for getting them up to speed on your criteria, past decisions, and terminology.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Which data sources would be most valuable to connect for your specific role?</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Reframing this to what <em>is</em> relevant for you: not org data sources, but your personal notes app (as you mentioned earlier) — that's the one connector that would meaningfully help your actual workflow.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">So in short: these three questions are worth revisiting only if your work shifts from solo to team-based. For now, your earlier connector answer (notes app) still stands as the one that matters.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start ml-0.5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-150"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" data-size="xs" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="_r_84_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-set